ZH: 公鸡在清晨叫醒了农夫。
EN: The rooster woke up the farmer in the early morning.

ZH: 公鸡是农村常见的动物。
EN: Roosters are common animals in the countryside.

ZH: 公鸡的叫声很响亮。
EN: The rooster's crow is very loud.

ZH: 农夫清晨起床时听到了公鸡的叫声。
EN: The farmer woke up to the sound of the rooster crowing in the morning.

ZH: 每天早上我都被公鸡叫醒。
EN: I am woken up by the rooster every morning.

