EN: The rooster is one of the symbols of the countryside.

ZH: 公鸡在村子里自由地跑来跑去。
EN: The rooster runs freely around the village.

ZH: 农夫在清晨赶去鸡舍喂养公鸡。
EN: The farmer rushes to the henhouse in the morning to feed the rooster.

ZH: 公鸡在树上喜欢打鸣。
EN: Roosters like to crow from the trees.

ZH: 农夫很爱他的公鸡。
EN: The farmer loves his rooster.

ZH: 公鸡喜欢在清晨喝水。
EN: The rooster likes to drink water in the morning.

